description: Rename pictures based on date Automatically change the name of images files taken by the camera based on the date and time when the file was created. Renamed and moved files process cannot be rolled back! Use this software with caution! The application does not store the old names because will cause conflicts: the default camera application use a counter which is reset each time when files are removed/renamed. As a workaround can be selected the option "Append original name".
